程序包 org.janusgraph.graphdb.query.graph

类 GraphCentricQuery

java.lang.Object
org.janusgraph.graphdb.query.BaseQuery
org.janusgraph.graphdb.query.graph.GraphCentricQuery
所有已实现的接口:
ElementQuery<JanusGraphElement,​JointIndexQuery>, ProfileObservable, Query
public class GraphCentricQuery
extends BaseQuery
implements ElementQuery<JanusGraphElement,​JointIndexQuery>
An executable ElementQuery for JanusGraphQuery. This query contains the condition, and only one sub-query JointIndexQuery. It also maintains the ordering for the query result which is needed by the QueryProcessor to correctly order the result.
作者:
Matthias Broecheler (me@matthiasb.com)
